{"tid":1612904,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"(聖旨到) 新華社: 香港警察以實彈槍擊示威學生, 完全合法合理正當","createTime":"2019-10-02T11:33:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T14:12:43.000Z","uid":134071,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"55322f91965ebb966bf0ee0a64b45891bcc13307","tid":1612904,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T11:33:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.cna.com.tw/news/acn/201910020106.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Facn%2F201910020106.aspx&d=zBKsoIV%2FeLhWSsP5H2J%2BmlKEWDR5zjN73Co06CeqttY%3D&h=5ce9d579\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.cna.com.tw/news/acn/201910020106.aspx</a><br />\n<br />\n首頁 / 兩岸<br />\n<strong>港警開槍 新華社：完全合法合理正當</strong><br />\n最新更新：2019/10/02 12:10<br />\n<br />\n（中央社記者邱國強北京2日電）港警昨天向高中生開槍成為眾矢之的，但中共官媒新華社今天發表評論，指香港持續3個多月的「黑色恐怖」已近瘋狂；又聲稱港警是被迫向襲警者開槍，「完全合法、合理和正當」。<br />\n<br />\n這篇題為「嚴正執法剜除暴力惡瘤」的評論宣稱，香港特區政府面對「紛爭」已釋出最大善意，並正努力透過多種方式解決當下爭端，第一場社區對話「也取得了積極成效」。<br />\n<br />\n評論說，「暴徒及其背後的勢力」絲毫沒有收斂，反而在中共建政70週年變本加厲，「以玉石俱焚的心態挑戰一切公序良俗，毫無理智可言」，嚴重影響香港民眾的人身安全和正常生活。香港正被他們「拖入巨大且可怕的泥淖中，付出極為沉重的代價」。<br />\n<br />\n這篇評論提到，在香港持續3個多月的「黑色恐怖」已近瘋狂。如果繼續容忍暴力，香港必然沉淪。止暴制亂，必須彰顯法治的力量，「剜除毒瘤，將所有暴徒儘快繩之以法」。<br />\n<br />\n評論聲稱，「黑衣人」是香港「最大的恐怖主義威脅」，而其「背後的操縱和指使者們」更應該被嚴正譴責。他們不斷洗腦年輕人，煽動他們走上街頭，目的就是以犧牲他人的方式破壞社會秩序，以達到自己「反中亂港」、奪取香港管治權的政治目的。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>至於昨天發生的港警向高中生開槍事件，評論宣稱，現場警員「生命受到嚴重威脅，為拯救自己和同事的生命，被迫向襲警者開了一槍」，行為「完全合法、合理和正當」。</strong><br />\n<br />\n（編輯：沈朋達）1081002"},{"pid":"284d0fd819998aa33cd827ce8e89510cec54f153","tid":1612904,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T11:33:35.000Z","msg":"咁弱智既評論, 睇怕可能係習總親自發出?<br />\n<br />\n信息中心: <br />\n-多篇狂屌香港示威者的文章, 都係出自習近平辦公室.  <br />\n-習近平&quot;批准&quot;政法委炮打李嘉誠<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hkhkhk.com/main/messages/20485.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkhkhk.com%2Fmain%2Fmessages%2F20485.html&d=zBKsoIV%2FeLhWSsP5H2J%2BmlKEWDR5zjN73Co06CeqttY%3D&h=cc50b4bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkhkhk.com/main/messages/20485.html</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hkhkhk.com/main/messages/20484.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkhkhk.com%2Fmain%2Fmessages%2F20484.html&d=zBKsoIV%2FeLhWSsP5H2J%2BmlKEWDR5zjN73Co06CeqttY%3D&h=cdf51d0b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkhkhk.com/main/messages/20484.html</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hkhkhk.com/main/messages/20508.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkhkhk.com%2Fmain%2Fmessages%2F20508.html&d=zBKsoIV%2FeLhWSsP5H2J%2BmlKEWDR5zjN73Co06CeqttY%3D&h=10b77b75\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkhkhk.com/main/messages/20508.html</a>"},{"pid":"64d5431e301fb2298bb79fdcd8bb764cb35987da","tid":1612904,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T11:34:10.000Z","msg":"有明確訊息證實係習近平一人當日堅持拒絕「撤回」及下令將44人極速起訴暴動！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1602129/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1602129/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"1b7550feadb6d81b6132535b48dc3713ce568603","tid":1612904,"uid":1426,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T11:34:14.000Z","msg":"64係啱，佢哋角度"},{"pid":"e6715613a41a57b6e90381d46405e8124212c404","tid":1612904,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T11:34:38.000Z","msg":"<strong>要俾美國政客睇到</strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbf719150feff9ed81d2ea7e1207cc8c6e1044e4","tid":1612904,"uid":155095,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"1b7550feadb6d81b6132535b48dc3713ce568603","tid":1612904,"uid":1426,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T11:34:14.000Z","msg":"64係啱，佢哋角度"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T11:36:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">大陸人思維：無鎮壓64中國就會好似蘇聯咁玩完</span>"},{"pid":"5485bb63c6ac84b159